data.description: 2.9% Assumable VA Loan  | Principal & Interest payment of $1,722.56 | Loan Balance of appx $386K..  Across the street from Oak Hills, Discover the epitome of perfection at 8165 Arrowhead Road, where the adobe design, ranch floor plan, and expansive lot seamlessly blend with the natural beauty of the high desert. This property, situated at the pinnacle of its nearly 2-acre lot, offers unrivaled views of the valley from its Southeast face. The spacious 2-car garage features a tandem door, opening to a versatile enclosed space – perfect for a workshop, gym, office, game room, or family room, providing endless possibilities. The distinctive arches within the interior add a touch of elegance, making this home truly unparalleled in the area. To top it off, a large concrete slab awaits to park your toys, complete with electricity. 8165 Arrowhead Road is not just a home; it's an extraordinary living experience that defies comparison in the high desert.
